{"data":[{"id":562373179,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a4a941cbe0340910bafc75bcb0304658","url_token":"du-li-ri-15","name":"蒋某人","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ad932547115d37623fd9af831f89f05_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ad932547115d37623fd9af831f89f05_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a4a941cbe0340910bafc75bcb0304658","user_type":"people","headline":"my left brain has nothing right \nmy right brain has nothing left","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":13,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562373179","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546080228,"updated_time":1546083344,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e这样吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我认为，哥德巴赫猜想很难，难到各位所说骑自行车上月球的难度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e反正我一个非数大一学生是看不懂啦\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e自认为高数能考几分，应该达不到知乎平均水平\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学上面天赋我是不咋地，我觉得啊，如果我高中钻研三年这东西，说不定能看出来点道道。(指比现在多看懂一点点)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e是的，我也不认为普通高中生有能力完成如此复杂的证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，我们对于题主的态度，是不是有点过于调侃，甚至有些恶意了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e是的，一个高中生不知道那东西多难，不知道自己可能伪证了什么东西。但是，有梦想有拼劲总是好的，为之努力过，奋斗过，也是光荣的。最起码，比看着别人失败，就发出哂笑的人，更光荣。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不否认许多民科的存在扰乱着现在各位科研大佬。 但我暂时还不能评价这位高中生是不是民科，不论他/她是学弟学妹，我都支持他。即使他证错了，我相信他能长教训，打好基础，为以后继续逐梦不屑奋斗。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他不就想问问能不能凭借证明哥德巴赫猜想能不能上清华北大吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e用得着这样子冷嘲热讽吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e来  我告诉你  可以!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有梦是好的，想证明自己是好的，为梦想不懈努力是好的，也许，他是个值得雕琢的璞玉呢?  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今天的他不能证明，也许这已经是定局了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是  我想问问你，二十年后的他呢?，四十年后的他呢? 我相信坚持的力量。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别再冷嘲热讽了，给题主梦想的种子一个发芽的空间吧！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e期待你的论文!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外  我不认为年龄与能力可以画等号\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年龄，很大程度上影响你的见识，你的经验，你的技巧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但这些，不是能力的全部。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别因为楼主的年龄再说三道四了好不好？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e半年前在看高中数学，又怎样？ \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e突飞猛进? 我虽然没见过谁进步这么快  但是说不定真的有呢?\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"这样吧我认为，哥德巴赫猜想很难，难到各位所说骑自行车上月球的难度。反正我一个非数大一学生是看不懂啦自认为高数能考几分，应该达不到知乎平均水平数学上面天赋我是不咋地，我觉得啊，如果我高中钻研三年这东西，说不定能看出来点道道。(指比现在多看懂…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1831\u